The key step is to write this new transaction in this book.
It goes through the resolution of a mathematical challenge to computers, and the winner of which, like a temporary central banker, will have the privilege of adding this extra line.
This is a phase of file hacking, i.e. transformation of a large file into a shorter and more unique fingerprint.
