In Israel, holy places, the Centre of the World and a sea of brine await Ukrainian tourists
The Promised Land brings together the greatness of Bible truths, modern comfort and a wild nature.
Argoumenty i Fakty has taken five great reasons to go to Israel.
Go and love the holy places
Make yourselves indispensable: the shores of the Jordan, where Jesus was baptized.
It is said that anyone who enters these "baptismal funds" will be touched by the Divine Grace.
As for Galilee, it is the land of the miracles of Jesus: where the water was changed into wine, where Jesus walked on water, where he calmed the storm, or where the fishing was miraculous.
