Sparkling stars.
You then hear the names of Jewish children and the names of countries in which they died.
Ukraine is also mentioned there.
Health and well-being
The three major resorts of Israel are located on the shores of the Mediterranean Sea, the Red Sea and the Dead Sea.
Each of them offers swimming pools, water parks, dolphinariums and giant aquariums.
Note: you can bathe in the Red Sea even in winter, because the water temperature does not fall below 21° while the air temperature can reach 23°.
The Dead Sea is even hotter and you can swim all year round.
By the way, it is the world's most unique sea: it occupies the lowest point on Earth, 417 m below sea level.
The water of azure color contains brine and very easily retains the bathers, even those who cannot swim.
The surrounding landscapes are surreal beauty.
It is there to perform a treatment based on salt water, lemon, curative sludge and to treat different diseases such as dermatitis, allergies, asthma, eczema, arthritis, bronchitis, diabetes but also simply to relax.
